title: Get Inbound Order
content:
# Path: /fbt/202409/inbound_orders
# Method: [GET]
# Function Description
This API is used to retrieve the inbound order details including the planned inbound detail, actual inbound detail and inbound status, etc.

---


# Common Parameters
For common parameters, refer to [How to call TikTok Shop APIs - Common Parameters](https://partner.tiktokshop.com/docv2/page/64f199679495ef0281851ee5#Back%20To%20Top)
| Properties <!-- width:110px --> | Location <!-- width:75px --> | Type <!-- width:75px --> | Require <!-- width:60px --> | Sample <!-- width:254px --> | Properties description <!-- width:254px --> |
| --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |
| shop_cipher | query | string | Y | GCP_XF90igAAAABh00qsWgtvOiGFNqyubMt3 | Use this property to pass shop information in requesting the API. Failure in passing the correct value when requesting the API for cross-border shops will return incorrect response. |
| Get by API [Get Authorization Shop](https://partner.tiktokshop.com/docv2/page/6507ead7b99d5302be949ba9?external_id=6507ead7b99d5302be949ba9) |  |  |  |  |  |
| content-type | header | string | Y | application/json | Allowed type: application/json |
# Request Query Parameters
| Properties <!-- width:110px --> | Type <!-- width:90px --> | Require <!-- width:90px --> | Sample <!-- width:254px --> | Properties description <!-- width:254px --> |
| --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |
| app_key | string | Y | 38abcd | Every single app will have a unique key. Please use the specific key assigned to your app. |
| sign | string | Y | 5361235029d141222525e303d742f9e38aea052d10896d3197ab9d6233730b8c | Signature generated by gen algorithm. When you send API requests to TTS, you must sign them so that TTS can identify the senders. |
| timestamp | int | Y | 1623812664 | Unix timestamp GMT (UTC+00:00). This timestamp is used across all API requests. Developers can use this convert to local time. |
| ids | []string | Y | 23230232324 | A list of inbound order IDs needs to be queried. The API will return the inbound order information for these IDs. |
| Note: The inbound ID consists of a series of numbers without the "IBR" prefix. |  |  |  |  |
| You can get the value in `data.inbound_order_id` in [Inbound FBT order status change](6708f866a88d1103246fed6a) webhook or in `data.inventory_records.order.id` in the response of [Search FBT Inventory Record](670d584ba83c5f030f3071e4). |  |  |  |  |
| shop_cipher | string | N | GCP_XF90igAAAABh00qsWgtvOiGFNqyubMt3 | Use this property to pass shop information in requesting the API. Failure in passing the correct value when requesting the API for cross-border shops will return incorrect response. Get by API [Get Authorization Shop](https://partner.tiktokshop.com/docv2/page/6507ead7b99d5302be949ba9?external_id=6507ead7b99d5302be949ba9) |
# Request Sample
**Query**
```Plain Text
https://open-api.tiktokglobalshop.com/fbt/202409/inbound_orders?app_key=123abc&sign=5361235029d141222525e303d742f9e38aea052d10896d3197ab9d6233730b8c&timestamp=1625484268&shop_cipher=ROW_RHkDDABBAAB8tKAVoAqsMTjsQZFLyNfY&ids=23230232324
```

# Response Parameters
| Properties <!-- width:110px --> | Type <!-- width:90px --> | Sample <!-- width:289px --> | Properties description <!-- width:289px --> |
| --- | --- | --- | --- |
| code | int | 0 | The success or failure status code returned in API response. |
| message | string | Success | The success or failure messages returned in API response. Reasons of failure will be described in the message. |
| request_id | string | 202203070749000101890810281E8C70B7 | Request log |
| data | object |  | Specific return information |
| ^inbound_orders | []object |  | A list of inbound order detail information. |
| ^^id | string | IBR23230232324 | The identifier for inbound order generated in Fillfilled by TikTok system. |
| ^^type | string | REPLENISHMENT | The inbound order type. |
| Possible values: |  |  |  |

* REPLENISHMENT |
   ^^merchant |object | |Merchant information. |
   ^^^id |string |493493403043 |The identifier of the merchant in Fulfilled by TikTok system. |
   ^^^name |string |ABC |The merchant name. |
   ^^create_time |int |1213232323 |The time when the inbound order created. Unix timestamp in seconds. |
   ^^ship_time |int |1213232323 |The time when the inbound order shipped. Unix timestamp in seconds. |
   ^^expect_arrive_time |int |1213243434 |The expected arrival time provided by merchant. Unix timestamp in seconds. |
   ^^actual_arrive_time |int |1213232323 |The actual arrival time. Unix timestamp in seconds. |
   ^^warehouse |object | |The warehouse information. |
   ^^^fbt_warehouse_id |string |121219993203023 |The Identifier for warehouse generated by Fulfilled by TikTok system. |
   ^^^warehouse_ids |[]string |["121219993209983"] |The identifier for warehouse generated by TikTok Shop system, will have the relationship with `fbt_warehouse_id`. |
   ^^^name |string |TikTok Warehouse |The Fulfilled by TikTok warehouse name. |
   ^^^type |string |PLATFORM_WAREHOUSE |The Fullfilled by TikTok warehouse type.
   Possible values:
* PLATFORM_WAREHOUSE |
   ^^planned_goods |[]object | |A list of planned goods details in the inbound order. |
   ^^^id |string |12324323 |The identifier for goods generated by Fulfilled by TikTok system. |
   ^^^reference_code |string |water01 |The identifier for goods defined by merchant. |
   ^^^name |string |100ml water |The Fulfilled by TikTok goods name. |
   ^^^quantity |int |9 |The planned goods quantity. |
   ^^^sku_ids |[]string |["1235566232323"] |The identifier for Stock Keeping Unit (SKU) generated by Fulfilled by TikTok system. |
   ^^received_batches |[]object | |A list of actual received inbound order batch details. |
   ^^^id |string |423541234612 |The identifier for inbound put away batch. |
   ^^^goods_id |string |12324323 |The identifier for goods generated by Fulfilled by TikTok system. |
   ^^^normal_quantity |int |9 |The quantity of normal goods in the inbound order batch. |
   ^^^defective_quantity |int |0 |The quantity of defective goods in the inbound order batch. |
   ^^^product_ids |[]string |["23455654676645"] |A list of product identifiers generated by TikTok Shop, which will be empty if the current goods do not match any product. |
   ^^^sku_ids |[]string |["1235566232323"] |A list of SKU (Stock Keeping Unit) identifiers generated by TikTok Shop, which will be empty if the current goods do not match any SKU. |
   ^^^total_quantity |int |9 |The total number of units received by the Fulfilled by TikTok warehouse in the inbound order batch, which is the sum of `normal_quantity` and `defective_quantity`. |
   ^^order_operation_logs |[]object | |A list of inbound order operation history. |
   ^^^operate_time |int |1715398048 |The time when the inbound order is processed by the merchant or warehouses, represented as a Unix timestamp in seconds. |
   ^^^order_status |string |RECEIVED |The order status in Fulfilled by TikTok warehouse.
   Possible values:
* WORKING
* READY_TO_SHIP
* TO_BE_RECEIVED
* ARRIVED_HUB
* INTERNAL_TRANSFER
* RECEIVING
* PARTIALLY_RECEIVED
* RECEIVED
* CANCELLED
* DELIVERED |
   ^^carriers |[]object | |A list of carrier information. |
   ^^^carrier_name |string |UPS |The carrier name. |
   ^^^tracking_number |string |3283298203923283943 |The tracking number for the current inbound shipment with the carrier. |

# Response Sample
```json
{"code":0,"data":{"inbound_orders":[{"id":"IBR23230232324","type":"REPLENISHMENT","merchant":{"id":"493493403043","name":"ABC"},"create_time":1213232323,"ship_time":1213232323,"expect_arrive_time":1213243434,"actual_arrive_time":1213232323,"warehouse":{"fbt_warehouse_id":"121219993203023","warehouse_ids":["121219993209983"],"name":"TikTok Warehouse","type":"PLATFORM_WAREHOUSE"},"planned_goods":[{"id":"12324323","reference_code":"water01","name":"100ml water","quantity":9,"sku_ids":["1235566232323"]}],"received_batches":[{"id":"423541234612","goods_id":"12324323","normal_quantity":9,"defective_quantity":0,"product_ids":["23455654676645"],"sku_ids":["1235566232323"],"total_quantity":9}],"order_operation_logs":[{"operate_time":1715398048,"order_status":"RECEIVED"}],"carriers":[{"carrier_name":"UPS","tracking_number":"3283298203923283943"}]}]},"message":"Success","request_id":"202203070749000101890810281E8C70B7"}
```
